Okay...so you want to see all those Apathy Boy comics that keep getting taken down? Okay.

2.) comment on this post so I'll friend you.

Myup. Friends only.

Hollerblock/mookie/lunchbox/fuck mook : DIE

Yes, I'm aware of the mispelling of "the".  That's deliberate, you ponce.  Tomorrow is my third to last day of art this year and I have no intention of getting any real work done...sooo expect a comic.

Tschus, mein Liebchens
